        <actionDate>2004-07-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2004-07-13T15:17:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Constitutional Amendment - </b>Federal Marriage Amendment - Declares that marriage in the United States shall consist only of the union of a man and a woman. </p> <p>Prohibits the Constitution or any State constitution from being construed to require that marital status or its legal incidents be conferred upon any union other than that of a man and a woman.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
